    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2210150/extras/0d3a75458b78877adf8d2640a0a0d788.poster.avif?t=1771259330\" width=600 height=369 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2210150/extras/0d3a75458b78877adf8d2640a0a0d788.webm?t=1771259330\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >挥舞你的利刃。与你的亲族唇枪舌战。决定你的命运。</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>《At Fate's End》</strong>是一款动作冒险游戏，你将与自己所爱之人展开战斗。扮演海姆洛克家族前途无量的年轻继承人——阿珊，挥舞传奇神剑伊索斯。探索纯手工绘制的、神秘莫测的奇幻世界，不断战斗，击败四处出现的邪恶生物。解决错综复杂的叙事谜题，揭开痛苦的真相，不断精进剑术和学识。在爱恨纠葛的决斗中，面对血脉相连，但早已疏离的兄弟姐妹——最终，决定家族的命运。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >用剑刃和话语战斗</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你的剑刃或许锋利无比，但你的旅程不只需要拔剑相向。通过对话技巧和心理洞察来控制局面，将你对家族秘密的深刻了解化为武器。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2210150/extras/06620c0dca146e6ce762bdd2cd13f9bc.poster.avif?t=1771259330\" width=600 height=392 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2210150/extras/06620c0dca146e6ce762bdd2cd13f9bc.webm?t=1771259330\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >你的技能树就是你的家族树</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你击败或和解的每一个兄弟姐妹，都会影响你的命运。收集七把力量之剑，扩充你的能力，最终决定你的家族传承。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >由《Spiritfarer》制作团队倾力打造</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >一手打造《Spiritfarer》的原班人马，在《At Fate's End》中编织出紧凑生动的游戏互动与丰富的叙事深度。身处刀剑碰撞不断、家族创伤深重的世界，纠缠于剪不断、理还乱的血缘联系之中。 </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >用你的剑刃战斗。为你的内心发声。面对你的亲人——当命运走到尽头。</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2210150/extras/3ef7d364b87de0decdf573c63f6356c2.poster.avif?t=1771259330\" width=600 height=113 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2210150/extras/3ef7d364b87de0decdf573c63f6356c2.webm?t=1771259330\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p>",
